import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"mri-dev-theme"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#mri-dev-theme"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`MRI DEV \${theme}`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`启动MRI THEME`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-bash"}}>{`\$ mri dev social
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"环境变量"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h3" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#环境变量"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`环境变量`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`环境变量跟随 UMIJS 的`}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":"https://umijs.org/guide/env-variables.html"}}>{`环境变量`}</MDXTag>{` `}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
